keyFacts: The email was sent on November 18, 2021, forwarding new intakes to a case file.
Three attached PDF documents are referenced with creation dates of November 14, 2021, and November 16, 2021.
The attachments contain information about individuals, including dates of birth and specific Eastern Time timestamps (4:24 PM, 1:52 PM, and 11:35 AM).
All personal identities in the document are redacted or protected (shown as PROTECT_IDENTITY).
The document is internal DOJ correspondence regarding case file updates.
